---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="More Info – Cara Colgate, LICSW" currentPage="info">
  <img class="upper-left"
    src="/images/office.jpg"
    alt="Welcoming therapy office with comfortable chairs and warm lighting"
  />
    <p>For address and contact information, please <a href="/connect/">click here</a>.</p> 
    <p>I also offer telehealth sessions for clients in Massachusetts.</p>

    <h2>Rates &amp; Insurance</h2>
    <p>My rate is $180 for a 53 minute session.</p>
    <p>I am currently empaneled by Blue Cross/Blue Shield. In addition, I am happy to provide you with an invoice or “super bill” to submit to your insurance company for reimbursement as an "out-of-network" provider. I recommend that you contact your health insurance company first to find out about your specific out-of-network coverage.</p>
    <p>Also note that Health Spending or Flexible Spending Accounts often consider therapy an approved expense.</p>

    <h2>Cancellation Policy</h2>
    <p>
      I save your appointment time for you. If you are unable to attend a session, please let me know 48 hours prior to the appointment to avoid being charged for the session.
    </p>
</Base>

<style>
  .info-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .office-image {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    position: sticky;
    top: 1rem;
  }

  .contact-link {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  section:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .info-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .office-image {
      max-width: 260px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: static;
    }
  }
</style>
